creator: forevertraveller@hotmail.com
text:
In FO, a table is nested into another table and the cell that table locates in 
has the property number-columns-spanned set to 3. If this property is removed, 
then all are OK and the produced PDF has more than one page. Or else  the FOP 
drops into the infinite loop.

creator: forevertraveller@hotmail.com
